e Change Control Board process.", "competency_name": "Customer / Value Orientation"}, "6": {"level": 6, "source": "pmt_customized", "customized": true, "level_name": "Mastering SE", "gap_percentage": 85.7, "objective_text": "Participants can set guidelines for models and write guidelines for good modeling, ensuring adherence to the V-Model development lifecycle and compliance with structured review gates. They will verify completeness of traceability links, consistency between SysML diagrams, and proper use of tools such as IBM Rhapsody for modeling and MATLAB/Simulink for simulation.", "competency_name": "Systems Modelling and Analysis"}, "7": {"level": 6, "source": "pmt_customized", "customized": true, "level_name": "Mastering SE", "gap_percentage": 100.0, "objective_text": "Participants are able to manage their relationships with colleagues and superiors in a sustainable manner within the context of the V-Model development lifecycle. They can resolve conflicts, bring different perspectives together, and negotiate sustainable compromises, particularly during structured review gates and the Change Control Board process for managing requirement changes.", "competency_name": "Communication"}, "8": {"level": 6, "source": "pmt_customized", "customized": true, "level_name": "Mastering SE", "gap_percentage": 100.0, "objective_text": "Participants are able to strategically develop team members so that they continue to develop when finding solutions, particularly in the context of the V-Model development lifecycle and through the use of tools like IBM DOORS Next Generation and IBM Rhapsody for effective requirements management and modeling.", "competency_name": "Leadership"}, "9": {"level": 6, "source": "pmt_customized", "customized": true, "level_name": "Mastering SE", "gap_percentage": 100.0, "objective_text": "Participants are able to work on complex projects, processes, and tasks in a fully self-organized manner while utilizing the V-Model development lifecycle and ensuring compliance with standards during model reviews. They can guide others in self-organization practices, particularly in managing requirements with tools such as IBM DOORS Next Generation and collaborating effectively using Jama Connect.", "competency_name": "Self-Organization"}, "10": {"level": 6, "source": "pmt_customized", "customized": true, "level_name": "Mastering SE", "gap_percentage": 100.0, "objective_text": "The participant is able to identify shortcomings in the V-Model development lifecycle process and make suggestions for improvement. They can successfully communicate reports, plans, and orders to all stakeholders and use advanced tool functions within IBM DOORS Next Generation, Jama Connect, and Microsoft Project Server.", "competency_name": "Project Management"}, "11": {"level": 6, "source": "pmt_customized", "customized": true, "level_name": "Mastering SE", "gap_percentage": 90.5, "objective_text": "Participants can evaluate decisions and establish overarching decision-making processes within the context of the V-Model development lifecycle. They can introduce decision methods company-wide, ensuring compliance with structured review gates and the Change Control Board process, and set up the decision management toolchain utilizing tools such as IBM DOORS Next Generation and IBM Rhapsody.", "competency_name": "Decision Management"}, "12": {"level": 6, "source": "template", "customized": false, "level_name": "Mastering SE", "gap_percentage": 100.0, "objective_text": "The participant can define a comprehensive information management process, establish documentation methods and standards, and set up the information management toolchain for the organization.", "competency_name": "Information Management"}, "13": {"level": 6, "source": "pmt_customized", "customized": true, "level_name": "Mastering SE", "gap_percentage": 100.0, "objective_text": "The participant is able to recognize all relevant configuration items within the context of the V-Model development lifecycle and build a complete configuration across all items. They can identify improvements, propose solutions, support others, and set up the relevant tool landscape, utilizing tools such as IBM DOORS Next Generation for requirements management and IBM Rhapsody for modeling.", "competency_name": "Configuration Management"}, "14": {"level": 6, "source": "template", "customized": false, "level_name": "Mastering SE", "gap_percentage": 90.5, "objective_text": "Participants are able to recognize shortcomings in the process and develop suggestions for improvement. They can guide colleagues in requirements formulation and introduce requirements tools to the enterprise.", "competency_name": "Requirements Definition"}, "15": {"level": 6, "source": "pmt_customized", "customized": true, "level_name": "Mastering SE", "gap_percentage": 85.7, "objective_text": "Participants can recognize shortcomings in the V-Model development lifecycle and develop suggestions for improvement. They can create and manage high-complexity SysML models using IBM Rhapsody, ensuring completeness of traceability links, consistency between diagrams, adherence to naming conventions, and proper use of stereotypes, while also setting up the toolchain for system modeling that includes IBM DOORS Next Generation and MATLAB/Simulink for simulation.", "competency_name": "System Architecting"}, "16": {"level": 6, "source": "pmt_customized", "customized": true, "level_name": "Mastering SE", "gap_percentage": 90.5, "objective_text": "The participant is able to set up a test strategy and test plans at an early stage, conduct design reviews in accordance with the V-Model development lifecycle, and establish verification and validation processes that comply with standards. They can optimize the test tool landscape for the organization, utilizing tools such as IBM DOORS Next Generation, Jama Connect, and IBM Rhapsody to ensure completeness of traceability links and adherence to modeling best practices.", "competency_name": "Integration, Verification, Validation"}, "17": {"level": 6, "source": "pmt_customized", "customized": true, "level_name": "Mastering SE", "gap_percentage": 90.5, "objective_text": "Participants are able to define the organizational processes for operations, service, and maintenance within the context of the V-Model development lifecycle, including standards compliance requirements, structured review gates, and the Change Control Board process for managing requirement changes, while utilizing tools such as IBM DOORS Next Generation and IBM Rhapsody for effective requirements management and modeling.", "competency_name": "Operation and Support"}, "18": {"level": 6, "source": "pmt_customized", "customized": true, "level_name": "Mastering SE", "gap_percentage": 90.5, "objective_text": "The participant can define and implement the relevant agile methods for a project using tools such as Jira Software for agile management. They are able to teach and introduce agile methods to others in the company, ensuring alignment with the V-Model development lifecycle and structured review gates.", "competency_name": "Agile Methods"}}, "strategy_comparison": {"by_competency": [{"status": "gap", "gap_size": 2, "target_level": 2, "competency_id": 1, "current_median": 0, "competency_name": "Systems Thinking"}, {"status": "gap", "gap_size": 1, "target_level": 4, "competency_id": 4, "current_median": 3, "competency_name": "Lifecycle Consideration"}, {"status": "gap", "gap_size": 1, "target_level": 2, "competency_id": 5, "current_median": 1, "competency_name": "Customer / Value Orientation"}, {"status": "gap", "gap_size": 1, "target_level": 4, "competency_id": 6, "current_median": 3, "competency_name": "Systems Modelling and Analysis"}, {"status": "gap", "gap_size": 1, "target_level": 4, "competency_id": 7, "current_median": 3, "competency_name": "Communication"}, {"status": "gap", "gap_size": 2, "target_level": 4, "competency_id": 8, "current_median": 2, "competency_name": "L