 have a basic awareness of Agile values and methods, which is a good starting point for further development.", "competency_name": "Agile Methods", "improvement_areas": "To progress to the required level, focus on learning how to define and implement Agile methods in projects. Participating in Agile training sessions, obtaining certifications, or joining Agile teams can provide you with the practical experience needed to motivate others and lead effectively in Agile environments."}], "competency_area": "Technical"}]	14
