ural models and methodologies. Engaging in peer reviews or mentorship opportunities can also help you further enhance your expertise."}, {"user_strengths": "You have a foundational awareness of the objectives of verification and validation, along with knowledge of various types and approaches to V&V.", "competency_name": "Integration, Verification, Validation", "improvement_areas": "To improve in this area, focus on developing your ability to read and understand test plans, test cases, and results. Consider taking a course on V&V processes or participating in projects that involve these activities to gain practical experience."}, {"user_strengths": "You are familiar with the stages of operation, service, and maintenance phases, and understand their importance in the development process.", "competency_name": "Operation and Support", "improvement_areas": "You meet the required level in this competency, so continue to build on this knowledge by staying updated on best practices in operation and support."}, {"user_strengths": "You have a basic awareness of Agile values and methods, as well as an understanding of the principles of Agile methodologies.", "competency_name": "Agile Methods", "improvement_areas": "To reach the required level, focus on deepening your understanding of Agile workflows and how to apply Agile methods in practice. Participating in Agile training sessions or workshops, and getting involved in Agile projects will help you gain the necessary experience to explain the impact of Agile practices on project success."}], "competency_area": "Technical"}]	17
