ility to define and implement relevant Agile methods for projects. Consider taking leadership roles in Agile teams to practice motivating others and advocating for Agile practices. Participating in Agile workshops or obtaining certifications can also enhance your skills and confidence in leading Agile initiatives."}], "competency_area": "Technical"}]	205
